+
+# Prune messages from g++ that aren't useful.
+
+proc prune_g++_output { text } {
+
+    # Cygwin warns about -ffunction-sections
+    regsub -all "(^|\n)\[^\n\].*: -ffunction-sections may affect debugging on some targets.*" $text "" text
+
+    return $text
+}
